text: LA-23 is a constituency of Azad Kashmir Legislative Assembly which is currently represented by the Shah Ghulam Qadir of Pakistan Muslim League (N). It covers the whole area of Neelum District of Azad Kashmir, Pakistan. Category:Neelam District ==Election 2016== elections were held in this constituency on 21 July 2016. Category:Government of Azad Kashmir Category:Constituencies of Pakistan
title: Constituency LA-23
